WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.700 --> 00:00:07.700
Come here.

2
00:00:07.700 --> 00:00:10.789
Help me tie my tie.

3
00:00:10.789 --> 00:00:12.789
You don't even know how to tie your own tie?

4
00:00:12.789 --> 00:00:15.820
Charlotte, you're not the noble Miss Bolton anymore.

5
00:00:15.820 --> 00:00:17.859
You need to remember you're my personal servant.

6
00:00:17.859 --> 00:00:19.890
Over my dead body.

7
00:00:19.890 --> 00:00:22.890
Listen, if you can't adjust to your new status,

8
00:00:22.890 --> 00:00:25.109
then not only will you face consequences,

9
00:00:25.109 --> 00:00:27.370
but your biological mother, Yolanda,

10
00:00:27.370 --> 00:00:29.910
she will also be kicked out.

11
00:00:29.910 --> 00:00:30.910
Now we made a deal.

12
00:00:30.910 --> 00:00:33.520
You served the Bolton family.

13
00:00:33.520 --> 00:00:36.520
And if not, we're going to sue you for everything you have.

14
00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:38.520
You don't mean that, Aaron.

15
00:00:39.899 --> 00:00:41.899
Just because she's not your biological mother

16
00:00:41.899 --> 00:00:43.899
doesn't mean she didn't raise you for 21 years.

17
00:00:43.899 --> 00:00:45.899
Does that mean nothing to you?

18
00:00:45.899 --> 00:00:49.950
If no idea what those years were like for me.

19
00:00:49.950 --> 00:00:55.130
Yolanda was abused by that drunken husband of hers.

20
00:00:55.130 --> 00:00:58.340
She couldn't protect me.

21
00:00:58.340 --> 00:01:00.340
It alone herself.

22
00:01:00.340 --> 00:01:04.719
My childhood was absolute hell, Charlotte.

23
00:01:04.719 --> 00:01:08.230
You don't know what that experience was like.

24
00:01:08.230 --> 00:01:11.519
Now just do what you're supposed to do and tie my tie.

